# Pre-existing transitive dependencies via kcl-lang.io/kpm (the KCL package
# manager kclipper uses to download charts): oras.land/oras-go's docker auth
# pulls in containerd/docker, and kpm's git downloader pulls in
# go-git/go-getter. Fixes require an upstream kpm release bumping these; they
# are not reachable from kclipper's own code paths.
